Lunarpine aproached Snow cat, she seemed hurt badly, he looked around for
any more help, not seeing any right away he Leans over the deseased bot.
"I'm sorry." he said under his breath placing a hand on her fur coat. He
pulls a few hairs out thinking about her sacrifice. "Your sacrifice will not
be forgotten, or in vain, I'll make sure of it." he stroked her fur a few
more times, "Yes you're right. Till all are one."

He stepped over to BlueStreak and picked him up. The bot seemed almost
weightless to Lunarpine. His new strength was just one of many new
improvements involved. He carried BlueStreak back to be repaired.

He returned to the Ark to check on Spears. He entered the CR  room. "Are
visiting hours up yet" he didn't know if she could recognize him but the two
had served together in the past and he thought it would only be right for
him to visit.
